Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.60,0:01:43.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常谢谢您
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.34,0:01:46.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚麻小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.46,0:01:48.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小凛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.90,0:01:49.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚沙前辈怎样了?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.86,0:01:55.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系 只要静养两三天的话就会复原了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.36,0:01:57.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.04,0:02:00.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以别太担心了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.91,0:02:01.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.15,0:02:06.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小凛有时间吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.57,0:02:08.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微谈一下话吧
